 The horsmen engaged the enemy preds. Apocalypse looked as they ran full 
speed into the fire. Famine shot several shots from his pistol. While Death 
Pull out his reaper and swung it at the first enemy pred he saw. War took 
cover behind a nearby boulder and every few seconds went up and fired a few 
shots at the oppostition.
